document_data.History:
Gordon assumed the throne of the High King in the {{YearlinkName|549}}, after slaying his own father, who had become infected with [[lycanthropy]].

In the [[562 DR|thirteenth year of his reign]], [[Anhaern Rhyllgallohyr]], Captain of the [[Sisters of Synnoria]] on [[Gwynneth]], died and returned to life as the "Shee" (short for "[[Banshee]] Rider").{{Cite dragon/362/Grand History of the Realms: The Moonshaes|26}}

Gordon ruled for twenty years before dying of [[disease|illness]] in the {{YearlinkName|569}}.
